---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - NEURO SYNAPSE">
	<article class="panel panel-container">
		<h1>About</h1>

		<section class="bio-section">
			<p>
				I'm a student researcher with a passion for neuroscience and science communication. While I do own a primary blog where I document my own research and life, I wanted to create a place where I could talk about cool neuroscience research in a more engaging and accessible way. The goal is to educate you, give valid sources for further reading and hopefully keep you entertained along the way.
			</p>
			
			<p>
				While I will cover a wide range of topics that I have an interest in, please do contact me with recommendations for new topics, changes to existing posts or just to say hi!
			</p>

			<p>
				I will be working on further updates when I catch the time and actual content!
			</p>
			<div class="contact-info">
				eikasia_ on discord (There is a secret guestbook page i'm not too happy with yet but it's there if you want to leave a message)
			</div>
		</section>
	</article>
</Layout>

<style>
	.panel h1 {
		color: var(--color-accent-red);
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--color-accent-yellow);
	}

	.bio-section p {
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.contact-info {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		padding-top: 2rem;
		border-top: 3px solid var(--color-dark);
	}

	.contact-info a {
		color: var(--color-accent-blue);
		border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-accent-blue);
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}

	.contact-info a:hover {
		color: var(--color-accent-red);
		border-color: var(--color-accent-red);
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.panel h1 {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}
	}
</style>
</Layout>
